column1: SDG 8.5 By 2030, achieve full and productive employment and decent work for all women and men,including for young people and persons with disabilities, and equal pay for work of equal value

Definition: Percentage of the labour force population ages 15 and older that is not in paid employment or self-employed but is available for work and has taken steps to seek paid employment or self-employment.
Source: ILO (2020). ILOSTAT database. https://ilostat.ilo.org/data/. Accessed 21 July 2020.

column2: Organization for Economic Co-operation and Development

column1: a: Estimates modelled by the International Labour Organization.
